MP3 Download: 04/2004 Jungle Mix

Once again, last night’s Selection 3 in ultramodern MP3 format; all the tunes, all the mixage, none of the DJ chatter. It was jungle this week, so grab yourself a 69.79MB VBR-encoded MP3 and let it rock ya dome, soundboy/girl. Many styles and eras represented, from Panacea’s jungle-cum-hardcore to the latin-tinged soundz of Visionary. Tracklist:

Artist – Track

  • Panacea – Motion Sickness
  • Photek – Knitevision
  • Jay – Sections
  • [unknown] – Side Alpha
  • Bad Company – Mo’ Fire
  • Ed Rush & Optical – EIB (remix)
  • Benjie – AI (Rawthang remix)
  • Bad Company – Dogsploitation
  • Visionary – Sola Bossa (feat. Sol Azul)
  • Ed Rush & Optical – Puerto Rico
  • Panacea – Nightmare Walking
  • [unknown] – Side Omega
